@startuml
[*] --> R1 : Receive video suggestion request from user
R1 --> R2 : Identify user who made the request
R2 --> R3 : Gather videos based on profile/preferences, trends, tags, genres, and promotions
R3 --> R4 : Add details (thumbnails, view counts) to suggested videos
R4 --> R5 : Send suggested videos to user
@enduml
